{
  "chapter": 104,
  "chapter_summary": "本章为大唐双龙传卷九第十章\"两代恩怨\"。徐子陵在鲁妙子处悟得\"遁走的一\"之玄理，返回住处时遭商秀洵持剑质问。商秀洵发现二人与李秀宁相识，又发现寇仲深夜持刀外出，遂将二人带至鲁妙子小楼对质。鲁妙子与商秀洵因旧日承诺产生争执，商秀洵限其十日内离开牧场。寇仲在追踪内奸时发现一荡妇与牧场中人勾结，并锁定商震为最大嫌疑。二人商议从奸夫入手调查。翌晨兰姑来催工，被寇仲以\"陪场主赏月\"为由唬住，徐子陵趁机要求改善生活条件。本章揭示了鲁妙子与商秀洵母亲的旧情，以及牧场内部潜伏的奸细危机。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你刚才到那里去了？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只是到后崖的小亭纳凉吧！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你那个好兄弟呢？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "text": "他的肚子不舒服，去了…嘿…场主明白啦！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你先把灯剔亮再说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "坐下！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你们与李秀宁是否旧相识？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "text": "谁是李秀宁？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你倒装得似模似样，以李秀宁的修养和镇定功夫，绝不会突然大惊小怪的。你还想瞒我，是否要家法侍候，始肯招供？这是敬酒不吃吃罚酒了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 65,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "text": "若场主不信任我们，我们明天便离开好了。纵使我们真的认识甚么李秀宁，亦没有触犯牧场的规矩。唉！我真不知怎么说才好呢。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "text": "场主！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 85,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "text": "场主定是想早点来欣赏我的宝刀哩！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你刚才到那里去呢？为何要拿刀子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "text": "刚才我和小晶…",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "text": "嘿！我和小晶到后山找那老先生学功夫，还吃了些东西，哈！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "甚么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 103,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你说甚么？忘了老先生吩咐吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "text": "老先生虽吩咐我们不可以告诉别人，可是场主是我们的老板，瞒甚么人都可以，却不该瞒她，小晶你真糊涂，还不向场主请罪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我只知大丈夫一言九鼎，说你吃了老先生的东西后拉肚子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "全都给我闭嘴。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你两个随我来。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_lu_miao_zi",
      "text": "老头儿！你违背诺言了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_miao_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鲁妙子",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "text": "场主已三年没有踏入我安乐窝的范围来，何不上来和老头儿喝一杯六果浆？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_lu_miao_zi",
      "text": "本场主没有兴趣，只知你违背承诺，究竟是你自己离开，还是要由我亲自赶走你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_miao_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鲁妙子",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "text": "我何处违背诺言呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_lu_miao_zi",
      "text": "三年前娘亲过世时，你在娘前亲口答应绝不管我牧场之事，又不会离开后山半步，所以我才肯让你留下来。现在你竟敢把所学传授予我牧场的人，不是违诺是甚么呢？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_lu_miao_zi",
      "text": "不准看我！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_miao_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鲁妙子",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "text": "你长得真像你娘。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_lu_miao_zi",
      "text": "不准你再提娘亲，你这种人根本不配谈她。到现在我仍不明白娘为何要至死都要维护你。好了！你究竟肯否和和气气的自己滚蛋。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_miao_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鲁妙子",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "text": "他们两个是你牧场的人吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_lu_miao_zi",
      "text": "他们是由我亲自聘用的，若不是牧场的人算甚么人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_miao_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鲁妙子",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "text": "三年之期未过，他们仍只是外人，唉！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_lu_miao_zi",
      "text": "鲁妙子，娘已死了，为何你仍恋栈不去呢？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_miao_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鲁妙子",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "text": "可否再给我十天时间，以后场主都不会再见到我了。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_lu_miao_zi",
      "text": "本场主就看在娘的份上，再予你十天宽容的时间。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你两个还不给我滚回去睡觉！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我发现了内奸。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你不是去找你的秀宁公主吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "本来真的想去找她，可是却碰上内奸。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你既去追那家伙，为何这么快便回来了。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "那家伙有种介乎绳索和飞梭间的攀山工具，能上落陡峭崖壁，我又不敢追得太近，几个照面就失了他影子，差点把我活活气死。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "所谓祸兮福所寄，若不是我及时赶回来，就要给美人儿场主拆穿了我们底细。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你还好说，摸肚子该代表拉肚子，却说甚么吃东西。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你又没装出拉肚子的表情，教我怎样分辨？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 213,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "今趟你显然选择错误，你若跟的是那个荡妇，现在就可知道谁是与外敌勾结的内奸！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "有这么多线索，还怕她可飞出我们的掌心吗？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "首先，这荡妇必是人家小妾一类的身份，且作了人家的小妾该没有多少天。其次给她骗的冤大头必是昨晚宴会上牧场方面的其中一个人，而有资格被称为老家伙的，便只有商震老头，梁治也可勉强凑上半脚。这么易查，有甚么么可怕的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "该以商震的可能性最大，不过这种事怎可随便查问。而且就算知道是谁，除非我们自揭身份，否则仍是奈何她不得。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我们就由那奸夫入手，他总要回来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "明天我们设法到那宅子看看，总该有些蛛丝马迹可寻。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "徐少爷似乎很关心美人儿场主，哈！我看她只是借头借路来亲近你吧。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你像是已浑忘了李秀宁，否则怎笑得出来呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "给那奸夫淫妇，加上美人儿场主先后一搞，我确把她暂时忘了。可见我这人确能提得起，放得下。是哩！我忘了问你鲁妙子传了你甚么手艺，是不是很好玩呢？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这确比弈剑术更玄妙，我们须好好研玩。还有甚么东西？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "有一事非常奇怪，商秀洵不是说过鲁妙子答应过三年内不得离开后山半步吗？但他明明不时溜了出去，定是有秘密通道，否则怎都会给发觉的。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "睡觉吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "兰姑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们昨夜去了做贼吗？知否现在是甚么时候了？整个牧场就只有你两个仍在睡觉。信否我进来把你们的床子拆掉呢？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "我们两人昨晚陪场主到后山赏月，谈了整晚，多睡一会都不行吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "兰姑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "场主…",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "你如不信就去问场主，看看我们有否陪她到后山去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 279,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不要吵了，起床吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "兰姑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "场主现在陪宁公主去了参观牧场，回来后宁公主就会到膳楼来看你们怎样弄熏鱼。这个是场主的吩咐，你们还不去准备一切了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "有些事我两兄弟真不明白，每趟兰姑来找我们，都要我们去做牛做马。但却从没有人告诉我们那处是澡堂，何处是茅厕。更不知一日三餐如何解决。场主昨晚便奇怪为何我们两名壮丁要挤在一张床上，这究竟谁该负上责任？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "所以今天我们决定怠工，除非生活得到大幅改善。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "兰姑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只是这两天特别忙，没时间理会你们罢了！你们先去梳洗更衣再说。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 104,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 305
    }
  ],
